    <sec>
      <title>3.3 GO analysis of neuronal differentiation</title>
      <p>GO enrichment analysis of mouse ESC differentiation to motor neurons in vitro (<xref rid="bty243-B17" ref-type="bibr">Mahony <italic>et al.</italic>, 2011</xref>) is shown in <xref ref-type="fig" rid="bty243-F4">Figure 4</xref>. The experiment has multiple GO terms identified as being significant. Rectangle color represents the relative significance, ranging from dark red (most significant) to bright yellow (least significant). The two lines show the GO identifier and a trimmed GO name.
</p>
